: formula_87
and is thus a tractrix.

The other involutes are not tractrices, as they are parallel curves of a tractrix.

=== Involutes of a cycloid ===

The parametric representation formula_88 describes a cycloid. From formula_89, one gets (after having used some trigonometric formulas)
